{"type": "article", "id": 2803, "title": "可折叠使用的电熨斗", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-13T07:16:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232608SLNJ3bZKY71P4RTo.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t熨烫衣物是个技术活儿，弄不好不但有可能烫伤衣物，亦有可能伤及自己。最近，美国设计师 Brandon Dierker 打造了一款便携折叠、易于操作的电熨斗 Collar Perfect ，使得都市中忙碌的年轻人也能够轻松操控。Collar Perfect 体积轻薄，折叠后仅为巴掌大小，出行时也方便携带和收纳它既可以当做常规的小型熨斗在平面上做整件衣物的熨烫，又可以折叠使用，用于重点处理领口、扣线、口袋、裤脚等易褶皱部位。五档温控设置适用于丝绸、羊毛、棉麻、牛仔等多种布料。目前，Collar Perfect 正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/699125038/collar-perfect-let-us-iron-out-the-wrinkles-in-you\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter </a>上众筹。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232605BDaPYpholHIziwgt.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232606J39cletEPF4MuzxH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232607MSbeRn3wkLPsdIiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}